    <p class="gem-c-title__context">
      Guidance
    </p>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Use of satellite decoder cards intended for EU audiences after the transition period
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Customers who access programmes via EU satellite broadcasting services to avoid a charge for a UK service will need to stop after the end of the transition period.</p>

  </div>
</div>

